<item>
 <title>Obama&#039;s Civil Rights Record in Foreign Policy</title>
 <link>http://www.brown.edu/Departments/Political_Theory_Project/janus/events/open_seminars/obamas_civil_rights_record_in_foreign_policy</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-type-datetime field-field-je-date&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;
